## üöÄ Installation

- Open the Extensions sidebar in VS Code
- Search for `Prop Star`
- Click Install
- Open the Command Palette with Ctrl+Shift+P or ‚áß‚åòP
- Select Preferences: Color Theme and choose `Prop Star Theme`.
